{
  "stem": "24651.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He died in 1978.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Texas.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He had open-heart surgery, and he died.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He-- my son has often said that he-- he didn't fear death, because he was so close to death so many times that he-- he didn't fear it.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, he was prepared.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I speak about my experiences to groups-- children mostly.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and I-- I hope that when I speak to kids, I let them know that it's so important to speak up when they witness any kind of discrimination-- to be sensitive, and to-- don't stand by.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Do-- you know-- be proactive.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] My feelings toward Germans or Germany, I've-- I've had-- it-- it's taken me a long, long time to really be in touch with my feelings, you know.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it's sort of like peeling an onion.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] I-- I have sort of mixed feelings.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I've been-- I've sort of made a circle where I'm just at total acceptance.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And now I'm-- I have a little-- a little fear and concern, and at times, a little discomfort with with Germany-- Germans or Germany.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, it's like, I want to know, you know, what's your position, or what--",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I have, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the first time I went, it was horrendous.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The second time I went, it was a little better.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Same thing when I went to visit Poland.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, when I-- first time I went, I didn't want to go to the museum.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I didn't want to enjoy myself, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I've met with my Polish family a couple times, and they're just so wonderful.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They're very exceptional people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They-- they had a-- another brother-- uncle of these children-- who was a priest.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He saved, I think, 200 Jews.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
